# FinTrack AI — Design System

## 1. Components — shadcn/ui only

```typescript
// ✅
import { Button } from "@/components/ui/button";
import { Dialog, DialogContent, DialogHeader, DialogTitle, DialogFooter } from "@/components/ui/dialog";
import { Select, SelectTrigger, SelectContent, SelectItem, SelectValue } from "@/components/ui/select";
import { Card, CardContent, CardHeader, CardTitle } from "@/components/ui/card";

// ❌ Never build custom modal, select, button, or input from scratch
```

All shadcn/ui components live in `client/src/components/ui/`. Do not install other component libraries.

## 2. Icons — lucide-react only

```typescript
import { Plus, Trash2, Pencil, TrendingUp, TrendingDown } from "lucide-react";
// ❌ No heroicons, react-icons, or SVG inlines
```

Standard sizes: `h-4 w-4` (default), `h-3.5 w-3.5` (compact), `h-5 w-5` (prominent).

## 3. Color tokens — use CSS variables, not hardcoded hex

```css
/* Design tokens from client/src/index.css (OKLCH) */
background: oklch(1 0 0)        /* white */
foreground: oklch(0.145 0 0)    /* near-black */
muted:      oklch(0.97 0 0)     /* light gray */
```

```typescript
// Budget color constants — use these values exactly
const BUDGET_COLORS = {
  green:  "#10B981",  // < 60% spent
  yellow: "#F59E0B",  // 60–85% spent
  orange: "#F97316",  // 85–100% spent
  red:    "#EF4444",  // > 100% spent
};
// Or use getBudgetProgressColor(pctUsed) from @/lib/utils
```

Never hardcode other hex values for status colors. Use Tailwind semantic classes (`text-emerald-600`, `text-red-500`, `text-amber-600`, `text-orange-500`) for text/badge status.

## 4. Typography

- **Font:** Inter (loaded via CDN in `client/index.html`) — do not change or override
- **Numbers:** always add `num tabular-nums` class on monetary/numeric values for consistent digit width
- **Headings:** `text-2xl font-bold tracking-tight` (page title), `text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-wide text-muted-foreground` (section label)

## 5. Layout & Spacing

- **Page wrapper:** `p-3 sm:p-6 max-w-5xl mx-auto space-y-4 sm:space-y-6`
- **Card grid:** `grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-3`
- **Responsive:** mobile-first — base styles for mobile, `sm:` for tablet+
- **DashboardLayout** wraps all routes — do NOT wrap a page in another layout

## 6. Theme

- **Light mode only** — no dark mode toggle per design spec
- Do not add `dark:` variants unless they already exist in the file
- Background is white; avoid colored page backgrounds
